reviewText: Corny teaches children about the dangers of strangers, it's very effective.
I was happy to find this video after many years. It is definitely a little be "corny" but the message is good STRANGERS TRAY MANY DIFFERENT WAYS TO TRICK KIDS.

I used to watch this over and over again just for Corny. But you know what? I actually learned a lot and didn't even know I was! I also can't wait to buy this for my kids. I know, firsthand, it's effective.
I loved this as a kid! I can't wait to buy this for my kids!
